This paper is primarily focused on neural style transfer, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new method for generating image transformation networks, which involves training a meta network, making it relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the efficiency of the proposed method, which could be relevant to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) subfields.
